{"id":328206,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/01/global-voices-乌克兰示威者向镇暴警察现场弹奏蓝侬的〈想/","date":"2014-01-04T02:30:30Z","modified":"2014-01-04T02:30:30Z","title":"Global Voices | 乌克兰示威者向镇暴警察现场弹奏蓝侬的〈想像〉","content":"<p><p>在这张美国音乐人与作曲家<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sean_Lennon\">西恩蓝侬</a>(<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Lennon\">约翰蓝侬</a>与小野洋子之子)脸书上所<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10152057500529431&#038;set=a.10152057501419431.1073741827.5438624430&#038;type=1\">分享</a>的照片里，一位钢琴家对着整排的镇暴警察弹奏约翰蓝侬的著名歌曲〈<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Imagine_(song)\">想像</a>〉。这张照片在一周内得到一万六千九百个赞并且被分享了六千一百次。</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10152057500529431&#038;set=a.10152057501419431.1073741827.5438624430&#038;type=1&#038;theater\"><img alt=\"A screenshot of Sean Lennon's Facebook Mobile uploads. The photo depicts a man playing \"Imagine\" in front of riot police in Kyiv, Ukraine.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Facebook-Imagine-400x216.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"216\"></a></p>\n<p>西恩蓝侬的脸书，照片中的男人在乌克兰的基辅对着镇暴警察弹奏〈想像〉。</p>\n</div>\n<p>这个概念与执行来自于无党派社运人士组织”<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hrom.sektor.euromaidan/posts/641483239223946\">Euromaidan’s Civic Sector</a>”的艺术行动，发生在持续进行中的乌克兰基辅EuroMaidan<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.kyivpost.com/hot/euromaidan/\">反政府抗议活动</a>中。</p>\n<div>\n<p>译者：PaoJ</p>\n<p>校对：Portnoy</p>\n</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/tetyana-bohdanova/\" title=\"文章导读 Tetyana Bohdanova\">Tetyana Bohdanova</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/gvzhteam/\" title=\"文章导读 GV 中文化小组\">GV 中文化小组</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/12/29/ukrainian-protesters-play-lennons-imagine-live-to-riot-police/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2014/01/04/13070/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br /><span><span>分享: </span> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%8B%E5%85%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E9%95%87%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%B9%E5%A5%8F%E8%93%9D%E4%BE%AC%E7%9A%84%E3%80%88%E6%83%B3%E5%83%8F%E3%80%89&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2014%2F01%2F04%2F13070%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2014%2F01%2F04%2F13070%2F&#038;desc=%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%8B%E5%85%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E9%95%87%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%B9%E5%A5%8F%E8%93%9D%E4%BE%AC%E7%9A%84%E3%80%88%E6%83%B3%E5%83%8F%E3%80%89\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2014%2F01%2F04%2F13070%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2014%2F01%2F04%2F13070%2F&#038;text=%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%8B%E5%85%B0%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E5%90%91%E9%95%87%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E5%BC%B9%E5%A5%8F%E8%93%9D%E4%BE%AC%E7%9A%84%E3%80%88%E6%83%B3%